con:config.con:query: SELECT CFS_INTRFC_ORD.MSG_TRNSMSN_ID AS TRANSMISSION_ID, CFS_INTRFC_ORD.CFS_INTRFC_ORD_ID AS TRANSACTION_ID, TO_CHAR( BLC_ORDER_PAYMENT.DATE_CREATED, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS ORDER_DATE, BLC_ORDER_PAYMENT.DATE_CREATED AS TRANSMISSION_DTTM, ETS_CUST_LNKG.LNKG_KY AS SOLD_TO_CUST_ID, BLC_CUSTOMER.LAST_NAME || ',' || BLC_CUSTOMER.FIRST_NAME AS SOLD_CUST_NAME, BLC_ADDRESS.ADDRESS_LINE1 AS BILL_TO_ADDRESS1, DECODE(BLC_ADDRESS.ADDRESS_LINE2, NULL,'',BLC_ADDRESS.ADDRESS_LINE2) AS BILL_TO_ADDRESS2, ETS_ADR.PSTL_LN_3_ADR AS BILL_TO_ADDRESS3, ETS_ADR.PSTL_LN_4_ADR AS BILL_TO_ADDRESS4, BLC_ADDRESS.CITY, BLC_ADDRESS.STATE_PROV_REGION, BLC_ADDRESS.POSTAL_CODE, ETS_CNTRY.ISO3_CNTRY_CDE, BLC_COUNTRY.NAME, CFS_INTRFC_ORD.ORD_SEQ_NO, CFS_INTRFC_ORD.ORD_PREV_SEQ_NO, BLC_ORDER.DATE_UPDATED, PGM.PGM_ABRV_NAM, ETS_DSCRT_ORD_ITM.PSFT_PROD_ID AS PRODUCT_ID, BLC_DISCRETE_ORDER_ITEM.BASE_RETAIL_PRICE AS LIST_PRICE, BLC_FULFILLMENT_GROUP_ITEM.QUANTITY AS QTY_ORDERED, BLC_ORDER_ITEM.PRICE*BLC_ORDER_ITEM.QUANTITY-DECODE(VCHR_PYMT.VCHR_VAL_AMT,NULL,0,VCHR_PYMT.VCHR_VAL_AMT)-DECODE(WAIVE_FEE_DTL.WAIVED_AMT,NULL,0,WAIVE_FEE_DTL.WAIVED_AMT) AS BILLED_AMT, BLC_ORDER_ITEM.PRICE*BLC_ORDER_ITEM.QUANTITY+DECODE(BLC_ORDER_ITEM_DTL_ADJ.ADJUSTMENT_VALUE, NULL, 0,BLC_ORDER_ITEM_DTL_ADJ.ADJUSTMENT_VALUE ) AS SALE_TRANS_AMT, BLC_ORDER_ITEM.ORDER_ITEM_ID AS SOURCE_LINE_NBR,--SOURCE_LINE_NBR,CUSTOM_C20_A ETS_DSCRT_ORD_ITM.PSFT_PROD_TYP_CDE AS CUSTOM_C10_A, --CUSTOM_C10_A BLC_ORDER_ITEM.ORDER_ITEM_ID AS CUSTOM_C20_A, BKNG.APNTMT_DT AS CUSTOM_C30_A, -- CUSTOM_C30_A(Test admin date) BKNG.TST_CNTR_ID_NO AS CUSTOM_C40_A, -- CUSTOM_C40_A (Test Site ID) BKNG.ETS_APNTMT_ID AS CUSTOM_C80_A, -- ETS_APNTMT_ID TEST Appointment ID --- OrdPay CFS_INTRFC_ORD.ORD_SEQ_NO AS TRANS_NBR, CFS_INTRFC_ORD.ORD_PREV_SEQ_NO AS TRAN_REF_NUM, PYMT_TRNSCTN.RCNCL_ID AS PAYMENT_ID, DECODE(BLC_ORDER_PAYMENT.PAYMENT_TYPE,'CREDIT_CARD','CCARD','PAYPAL','PAYPAL','PAPER_CHECK','CHECK','ELECTRONIC_CHECK','ECHECK','ZERO_AMOUNT','NONE') AS PYMNT_METHOD_FLD, DECODE( (SELECT FIELD_VALUE FROM BLC_PAYINFO_ADDITIONAL_FIELDS WHERE BLC_ORDER_PAYMENT.PAYMENT_ID = BLC_PAYINFO_ADDITIONAL_FIELDS.PAYMENT_ID AND FIELD_NAME='CARD_TYPE'),'Visa','VISA') AS CC_CARD_TYPE, PYMT_TRNSCTN.DATE_CREATED AS TRANSACTION_DTTM, ABS(PYMT_TRNSCTN.AMT) AS TRANSACTION_AMT, DECODE(PYMT_TRNSCTN.PRSNTMNT_AMT, NULL,0,PYMT_TRNSCTN.PRSNTMNT_AMT) AS PAID_AMT_BSE, DECODE(PYMT_TRNSCTN.PRSNTMNT_CRNCY_CDE,NULL,' ',PYMT_TRNSCTN.PRSNTMNT_CRNCY_CDE) AS CURRENCY_CD_BSE, DECODE(PYMT_TRNSCTN.PRSNTMNT_FGN_EXCHG_RT,NULL,0,PYMT_TRNSCTN.PRSNTMNT_FGN_EXCHG_RT) AS FX_SPOT_RATE, PYMT_TRNSCTN.PYMT_TRNSCTN_ID AS PAY_TRANS_ID, DECODE(PYMT_TRNSCTN.PYMT_INSTRMNT_ID, NULL,'NA',PYMT_TRNSCTN.PYMT_INSTRMNT_ID) AS CHECK_NBR FROM BLC_ORDER, CFS_INTRFC_ORD, PYMT_TRNSCTN, ETS_CUST_LNKG, BLC_CUSTOMER, BLC_ORDER_PAYMENT, BLC_ADDRESS, ETS_ADR, BLC_COUNTRY, ETS_CNTRY, BLC_CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, BLC_ORDER_ITEM, BLC_DISCRETE_ORDER_ITEM, ETS_SKU, PGM, ETS_DSCRT_ORD_ITM, BLC_FULFILLMENT_GROUP_ITEM, VCHR_PYMT, WAIVE_FEE_DTL, BLC_ORDER_ITEM_PRICE_DTL, BLC_ORDER_ITEM_DTL_ADJ, TST_DSCRT_ORD_ITM_BKNG, BKNG WHERE CFS_INTRFC_ORD.ORD_ID = BLC_ORDER.ORDER_ID AND BLC_ORDER.ORDER_ID = PYMT_TRNSCTN.ORDER_ID (+) AND BLC_ORDER.CUSTOMER_ID = ETS_CUST_LNKG.CUSTOMER_ID AND ETS_CUST_LNKG.LNKG_TYP_CDE = 'DSPID' AND BLC_ORDER.CUSTOMER_ID = BLC_CUSTOMER.CUSTOMER_ID AND BLC_ORDER.ORDER_ID = BLC_ORDER_PAYMENT.ORDER_ID AND BLC_CUSTOMER_ADDRESS.CUSTOMER_ID =BLC_CUSTOMER.CUSTOMER_ID AND BLC_CUSTOMER_ADDRESS.ADDRESS_ID =BLC_ADDRESS.ADDRESS_ID AND BLC_ADDRESS.ADDRESS_ID = ETS_ADR.ADDRESS_ID AND BLC_ADDRESS.COUNTRY =BLC_COUNTRY.ABBREVIATION AND BLC_COUNTRY.ABBREVIATION =ETS_CNTRY.CNTRY_CDE AND BLC_ORDER_ITEM.ORDER_ID = BLC_ORDER.ORDER_ID AND BLC_ORDER_ITEM.ORDER_ITEM_ID = BLC_DISCRETE_ORDER_ITEM.ORDER_ITEM_ID AND BLC_DISCRETE_ORDER_ITEM.SKU_ID =ETS_SKU.SKU_ID AND ETS_SKU.PGM_CDE =PGM.PGM_CDE AND BLC_ORDER_ITEM.ORDER_ITEM_ID =ETS_DSCRT_ORD_ITM.ORDER_ITEM_ID AND BLC_ORDER_ITEM.ORDER_ITEM_ID =BLC_FULFILLMENT_GROUP_ITEM.ORDER_ITEM_ID AND BLC_ORDER_ITEM.ORDER_ITEM_ID =VCHR_PYMT.ORDER_ITEM_ID(+) AND BLC_ORDER_ITEM.ORDER_ITEM_ID =WAIVE_FEE_DTL.ORDER_ITEM_ID(+) -- BILLED_AMT AND BLC_ORDER_ITEM.ORDER_ITEM_ID =BLC_ORDER_ITEM_PRICE_DTL.ORDER_ITEM_ID (+) AND BLC_ORDER_ITEM_PRICE_DTL.ORDER_ITEM_PRICE_DTL_ID =BLC_ORDER_ITEM_DTL_ADJ.ORDER_ITEM_PRICE_DTL_ID(+) -- SALE_TRANS_AMT AND BLC_ORDER_ITEM.ORDER_ITEM_ID=TST_DSCRT_ORD_ITM_BKNG.ORDER_ITEM_ID(+) AND TST_DSCRT_ORD_ITM_BKNG.BKNG_ID = BKNG.BKNG_ID (+) --AND BLC_ORDER_PAYMENT.PAYMENT_ID = BLC_PAYINFO_ADDITIONAL_FIELDS.PAYMENT_ID --AND BLC_PAYINFO_ADDITIONAL_FIELDS.FIELD_NAME='CARD_TYPE' AND BLC_ORDER.ORDER_ID = ${Properties#orderNumber}

SELECT BLC_FULFILLMENT_GROUP_ITEM.QUANTITY AS QTY, ETS_CNTRY.ISO3_CNTRY_CDE AS COUNTRY, BLC_COUNTRY.NAME AS COUNTRY_NAME, BLC_ADDRESS.ADDRESS_LINE1 AS ADDRESS1, BLC_ADDRESS.ADDRESS_LINE2 AS ADDRESS2, ETS_ADR.PSTL_LN_3_ADR AS ADDRESS3, ETS_ADR.PSTL_LN_4_ADR AS ADDRESS4, BLC_ADDRESS.CITY AS CITY, BLC_ADDRESS.STATE_PROV_REGION AS STATE, BLC_ADDRESS.POSTAL_CODE AS POSTAL, --- OrdLineSchdTax BLC_TAX_DETAIL.TYPE AS TAX_JURISDICTION, DECODE(ETS_TAX_DTL.TAX_JRSDTN_NAM, NULL,'NA',ETS_TAX_DTL.TAX_JRSDTN_NAM) AS TAX_JUR_NAME, BLC_FULFILLMENT_GROUP_ITEM.TOTAL_ITEM_TAXABLE_AMOUNT AS TAX_BASIS_AMT, BLC_TAX_DETAIL.RATE AS TAX_PCT, BLC_TAX_DETAIL.AMOUNT AS TAX_AMT FROM BLC_ORDER,BLC_ORDER_ITEM,BLC_FULFILLMENT_GROUP_ITEM, BLC_FULFILLMENT_GROUP,BLC_ADDRESS,BLC_COUNTRY,ETS_CNTRY,ETS_ADR,BLC_FG_ITEM_TAX_XREF,BLC_TAX_DETAIL, ETS_TAX_DTL WHERE BLC_ORDER_ITEM.ORDER_ITEM_ID=BLC_FULFILLMENT_GROUP_ITEM.ORDER_ITEM_ID AND BLC_ORDER_ITEM.ORDER_ID = BLC_ORDER.ORDER_ID AND BLC_ORDER.ORDER_ID=BLC_FULFILLMENT_GROUP.ORDER_ID AND BLC_FULFILLMENT_GROUP.ADDRESS_ID=BLC_ADDRESS.ADDRESS_ID AND BLC_ADDRESS.ADDRESS_ID=ETS_ADR.ADDRESS_ID AND BLC_ADDRESS.COUNTRY=BLC_COUNTRY.ABBREVIATION AND BLC_COUNTRY.ABBREVIATION=ETS_CNTRY.CNTRY_CDE AND BLC_FULFILLMENT_GROUP_ITEM.FULFILLMENT_GROUP_ITEM_ID=BLC_FG_ITEM_TAX_XREF.FULFILLMENT_GROUP_ITEM_ID AND BLC_FG_ITEM_TAX_XREF.TAX_DETAIL_ID=BLC_TAX_DETAIL.TAX_DETAIL_ID AND BLC_TAX_DETAIL.TAX_DETAIL_ID=ETS_TAX_DTL.TAX_DETAIL_ID AND BLC_ORDER.ORDER_ID = ${Properties#orderNumber}
